lead_paragraph: Aqib Talib returned to the Denver Broncos' headquarters on Wednesday so team doctors could evaluate his gunshot wound after a bullet pierced his right thigh and calf last weekend.

headline.print_headline: Broncos CB Aqib Talib Will Have to Stay in Denver
